{"tid":2309151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國際特赦斥香港政府控告知名社運人士旨在殺雞儆猴","createTime":"2020-12-02T10:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T12:01:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d78edf457d6b20966ec9da9fb89f489be2ac959","tid":2309151,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T10:51:29.000Z","msg":"前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒、主席林朗彥及成員周庭，去年6月21日包圍警總的案件，3人今日在西九龍裁判法院分別判處監禁，即時入獄。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織亞太區域主任Yamini Mishra表示，香港政府再次出於政治動機，以「煽惑他人參與未經批准集結」等罪名，起訴以和平方式表達訴求和示威的人士。<br />\n<br />\n組織批評當局在這些「無大台」的示威活動中，選擇控告知名社運人士，旨在殺雞儆猴。3人被判監，侵害了他們的表達自由及和平集會權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563226-20201202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563226-20201202.htm&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=2e9fc97b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563226-20201202.htm&h=14533c47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563226-20201202.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3a4b72620763c08084ca2a7c614e76d47dadd30e","tid":2309151,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2892befe6d1a82f6a6744f4c839b6b74ba7654","tid":2309151,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d8fb57487769e064de8bd116528ee73791b89e","tid":2309151,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj